    "body": "To be more explicit: What should happen when the specified `container` key resolve to several DOM elements. Should they all get rendered or only the first one.\n\nUse-case is adding several widgets such as \"XXX result in YYY ms\" or \"Order by\" at the top and bottom of the search results.\n\nI'd go with all the matching elements\n",
